<P>
<I>First Marathon Securities has completed the private placement of 8 million special warrants for Goldbelt, raising C$8.4 million for the company. In May the market responded very favorably to results released by the company from its second step-out drill hole on the Abyz copper/gold deposit in Kazakstan. These drill holes show a continuance of the high grade intercept and further extends the known resource. Goldbelt has moved a diamond
drilling rig onto its 100% owned Kakbit deposit where previous trench samples have uncovered a number of highly prospective gold, silver, copper and zinc anomalies. Stay closely in touch for additional drill results in the near future.</I>
