<P>
<TITLE>TOP TEN BOOK #1</TITLE>
<P>
<P>
<H2> Reminiscences of a Stock Operator</H2>
<P>
 Edwin Lefevre, 299pp, 
<P>
Item #2116 -- flexible cover -- $19.95US<BR>
Item #2117 -- deluxe hardcover edition -- $ 34.95US<BR>
<P>
<P>
This all-time best-seller market classic tells the inside story of Jesse Livermore, one of the greatest speculators ever.  This all-time-bestseller clearly details the attitudes, reactions and feelings that all traders have. Written in 1923, tells the day to day story of Jesse Livermore.Learn more about yourself and the markets from this book than from years in the market.
<P>
<P></BODY>
