<HR>
<P>
<TITLE>TOP TEN BOOK #2</TITLE>
<P>
<P>
<H3>Alchemy of Finance </H3>
<P>
<H2>"Reading the Mind of the Market"</H2>
<P>
<P>
 George Soros,  384pp, 
<P>
Item #3570 -- flexible cover -- $19.95US<BR>
Item #3569 -- hard cover -- $39.95US<BR>
<P>
George Soros is known as the most powerful and profitable investor in the world.  His Quantum Fund made an astonishing $ 1.1 billion in a single month.
<P>
The <I>Alchemy of Finance</I> is more than a guide to the inner workings of financial markets.  In it, Soros reveals the secrets of his investment strategy and gives his opinions and prediction on current financial trends. Includes his innovative "theory of reflexivity", which underlies not only the investment strategies which have made him "a superstar among money managers" (NY Times), but also his unique view of world events.
<P>
<P>
"An extraordinary...inside look into the decision making process of the most successful money manager of our time. Fantastic!"-The Wall Street Journal.
<P>
<P></BODY>
</HTML>


