 <P>
<TITLE>TOP TEN BOOK #3</TITLE> 
<P>
<P>
<H2> The New Market Wizards</H2>
<P>
<P>
Jack Schwager, 493pp,
<P>
Item #2106 -- $35US<BR>
<P>
Meet the next generation of market killers. These spectacular winners often make millions of dollars - sometimes in hours - consistently outperforming their peers.   Hear the private tactics of Gil Blake, a virtual unknown fund timer who, over a 12 year period realized a 45% annual return.  William Eckhardt, the little-known mathematician who helped Richard Dennis develop the Turtle Trading System, and more.  They trade across the spectrum of financial markets, using vastly different tactics, but all share remarkable successes.  What are their secrets?  How can you mirror their success?  Here is your chance to learn from today's greatest trading minds. 
<P>
<P></BODY>
</HTML>



 
