<P>
<H3>Trader Vic II </H3>
<P>
<H2>"Principles of Professional Speculation"</H2>
<P>
<P>
 Victor Sperandeo,  400pp, 
<P>
Item #2251 -- $37.50US<BR>
<P>
Trader Vic's first book introduced you to this wildly successfull trader and his tremendous achievements.
<B>NOW</B>, Vic has been convinced to reveal the inner workings of his trading systems.  This all new book offers a comprehensive description of the systems that underlie his powerful approach.  You'll read his secret analysis methods including fresh uses of Dow Theory, technical analysis, risk assessment and forecasting.  Learn to combine technical and fundamental methods into a razor sharp system.  Read fresh ideas on probability, politics, economics, and psychology all designd to enhance your trading profits.  Don't miss this latest classic from "one of today's greatest professional traders."
<P>
