<TITLE>TOP TEN BOOK #8</TITLE> 
<P>
<P>
<H2>Options as a Strategic Investment</H2>
<P>
<B>3rd Edition</B>
<P>
 Lawrence McMillan, 884pp<BR>
<P>
Item #2836 -- $49.95US<BR>
<P>
<P>
Undisputed Bible of option trading explains virtually every aspect of options trading in terms that the average trader can apply immediately. Complete explanantions of dozens of option strategies with full commentary on when and when not to use them. Learn how to gauge the true value of an option and how to tell if a contract is over-priced. McMillan details how to use volatility and pricing tactics to increase profits.  Contains over 100 pages of option strategies, full run-downs of LEAPS, CAPS, and much more. If you're looking to increase your option profits, buy this book.
<P>
<P></BODY>
