<HTML>

<HEAD>

   <TITLE>1997 Carleton Library Staff Directory</TITLE>

   <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Mozilla/3.0Gold (Win95; I) [Netscape]">

</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">



<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>1997 Carleton Library Staff Directory</H1>

<A HREF="stafftext.html">text version of the staff directory</A>

<UL>

<LI><A HREF="#admn">Administration</A> </LI>



<LI><A HREF="#acq">Acquisitions &amp; Serials</A> </LI>



<LI><A HREF="#arch">Archives</A> </LI>



<LI><A HREF="#cat">Cataloging</A> </LI>



