<TITLE>Student Jobs in the Carleton Library</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<CENTER><H2>Student Job Openings in the Carleton Library</H2></CENTER>
<p>
We rely on the talents of student employees to offer the best possible library services.  
Here is a list of currently available openings in various library departments:
<p>
<ul>
<li>Aquisitions
<li>Cataloging
<li><a href="circjob.html">Circulation</a>
<li><a href="govdocjob.html">Government Publications</a> (computer-related)
<li>Information Services
<li>Interlibrary Services
<li>Preservation
<li><a href="circjob.html#rese">Reserves</a>
<li>Science Library
<li><a href="sysjob.html">Systems</a> (computer-related)
</ul>
<P>
