<Title>Circulation Desk Employment</title>

<body BGCOLOR="FFFFF0">
<h2><center>Student Job Opportunites with Circulation</center></h2>
<br>
<a href="#circ">Circulation Desk Student Worker</a>
<br>
<a href="#rese">Reserves Desk Student Worker</a>
<br>
<a href="#shel">Shelving Student Worker</a>
<p>
<a href="#how">How to Apply</a>
<br>
<hr>
<a name="circ">
<h3>Circulation Desk Student Worker</h3>
<br>
<strong>Purpose of Position:</strong> 
<ul>
<li>Check in and check out library materials (including books,
magazines,   government documents, audio cassettes, maps) to patrons
<li>Assist with issuing barcodes to patrons
<li>Assist patrons in placing searches/recalls and renewing library material
<li>Help locate library materials
<li>Inform patrons about library services
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Qualifications:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Familiarity with campus and library
<li>Excellent phone and personal communication skills
<li>Self-motivated, dependable, and responsible
<li>Ability to use discretion and judgment in a variety of situations
<li>At least 8 hour work contract, willing to work days, evenings, and weekends
</ul>
<br>
<hr>
<a name="rese">
<h3>Reserves Desk Student Worker</h3>
<br>
<strong>Purpose of Position:</strong>
<ul> 
<li>Maintain the Reserves Area by checking in and out Reserve items
<li>Explain Reserve procedures to patrons and answer general questions
<li>Shelve returned reserve items
<li>Keep the Reserves Area orderly and organized
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Qualifications:</strong>
<UL>
<li>Excellent personal communication skills
<li>Self-motivated, dependable, and responsible
<li>Ability to use discretion and judgment in a variety of situations
<li>At least 8 hour work contract, willing to work days, evenings, and weekends
</ul>
<br>
<hr>
<a name="shel">
<h3>Shelving Student Worker</h3>
<br>
<strong>Purpose of Position:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Shelve books in stacks and sort books that belong in special collections
<li>Keep the stacks neat and orderly
<li>Inventory the stacks for misshelved books.
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Qualifications:</strong> 
<ul>
<li>Self-motivated, dependable, and responsible
<li>At least a six-hour work contract, willing to work weekdays between 8 and 5
</ul>
<br>
<hr><br>
<a name="how">
<strong>How to Apply:</strong> Contact <a href="mailto:jedwins@carleton.edu">Jennifer Edwins</a> at the front desk in the
main library between 8 am and 3 pm Monday - Friday.
<br>
<br><hr>
This page last updated on March 5, 1996 by <a href="/staff/terry/terry.html">Terry Metz</a> and his staff.
</body>
