<head><title>Carleton College Library - Classics</title>
</head>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<center><H1>Classics Resources Available in the Carleton College Library</H2></center>
<center><H4>Fall 1996, Prof. Clayton Zimmerman</H4></center><br>

<H3>Muse - Online Catalog</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.library.carleton.edu/muse/muse.html">About Muse</A>
<LI><A HREF="telnet://muse.library.carleton.edu">Jump Directly to Muse</A>
</UL>

<H3>Electronic Indexes and Abstracts</H3>
<ul>
<LI><A HREF="/electronic/online/firstsearch.html">FirstSearch</A>
<LI><A HREF="/electronic/cd-rom/cd-rom.html#hist">Historical Abstracts</A> (CD-ROM)
<LI><A HREF="/electronic/online/mla.html">MLA International Bibliography</A>
