David Clark Cabeen, general editor. <strong>A Critical Bibliography of French Literature</strong>. 1947- .
<DD>Annotated bibliography describing books, articles and dissertations with references to reviews of works mentioned in certain cases.  Each volume of this extensive set has its own index.

