<DT><kbd>PQ 35 .F73</kbd><br>
by the French Institute-Alliance Francaise, New York and the Camargo Foundation, Cassis, France. <strong>French XX Bibliography</strong>. 1969- .
<DD>A bibliography of criticisms on French literature of the 20th century (really from 1885-  ).  Has a multi-part arrangement.  Part One covers subjects of a general nature such as genres, history, philosophy, symbolism, etc.  Part Two covers individual authors and their works.  In later volumes Part Three is available covering Film.  The first section is on general film study and the second section on directors, actors, and authors.  Note that a separate index of personal names from the years 1949-1988 was published and is kept on the same shelf in Reference. 

