<DT>WEEK 6: <U>Oral Paper Reports</U> </DT>
<DD><UL>
    <LI>Mon., Feb. 10: Mid-term break </LI>
    <LI>Wed., Feb. 12: <U>Oral Paper Reports</U> </LI>
    <LI>Fri., Feb. 14: <U>Oral Paper Reports</U> </LI>
    </UL>
</DD>
<DT>WEEK 7: <U>Margaret Fuller</U> </DT>
<DD><DL>
    <DT>Mon., Feb. 17: <U>The Life of Margaret Fuller</U> </DT>
    <DD><UL>
        <LI><IMG SRC="/images/greenball.gif" ALT="*" HIEGHT="14" WIDTH="14"> Eve Kornfeld, <U>Margaret Fuller: A Brief Biography with Documents</U> (1997), Preface and Part One (Chaps. 1-7).</LI>
        <LI><IMG SRC="/images/greenball.gif" ALT="*" HIEGHT="14" WIDTH="14"> Richardson, Chaps. 39, 56, 82.</LI>
        </UL>
