    <DD><UL>
        <LI><IMG SRC="/images/greenball.gif" ALT="*" HIEGHT="14" WIDTH="14"> Kornfeld, Document 26, &quot;Woman in the Nineteenth Century.&quot;</LI>
        </UL>
    <DT>Fri., Feb. 21: <U>Seminar Project: A Margaret Fuller-Style Transcendental Conversation</U> </DT>
    <DD>Note: See Part One of syllabus for <A HREF="#conversation">instructions and readings</A>. </DD>
    </DL>
</DD>
<DT>WEEK 8: <U>Race, Romantics, and Some Other Transcendentalists</U> </DT>
