    <DD><UL>
        <LI><IMG SRC="/images/greenball.gif" ALT="*" HIEGHT="14" WIDTH="14"> Henry David Thoreau, <U>A Plea for Captain John Brown</U> (1860), in Henry David Thoreau, <U>Civil Disobedience and Other Essays</U>, 31-48.</LI>
