            <LI>&quot;When Lilacs Last in the Dooryard Bloom'd&quot;</LI>
            <LI>&quot;O Captain! My Captain!&quot;</LI>
            </UL></LI>
        </UL>

    <DT>Wed., Mar. 12: <U>Legacy of the Transcendentalists and The Summing Up</U> </DT>
    <DD><UL>
