<H3>Sample Web Links for Music Research</H3>
<P>
<DL>
<DL>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.altavista.digital.com/cgi-bin/query?pg=q&what=web&fmt=.&q=%28music+history%29">Alta Vista: Music History Links</A>
    and <A HREF="http://www.altavista.digital.com/cgi-bin/query?pg=q&what=web&fmt=.&q=%28music+theory%29">Alta Vista: Music Theory Links</A>
<DD>Alta Vista is one of the premier search engines on the Web.  Here is a list of links produced by a search using the
terms "music history" and "music theory".
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Entertainment/Music/History/">Yahoo:Entertainment:Music:History</A> 
    and <A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Entertainment/Music/Theory/">Yahoo:Entertainment:Music:Theory</A>
<DD>Yahoo is one of the primier directories of Internet resouces.  Here you'll find links to resources on 
"music history" and "music theory".
<P>
</DL>
</DL>
