<!-- ###############Bibliographies  -->
<a name="biblio">
<h3>Bibliographies</h3>

Bibliographies are lists of materials on a particular topic.  They should save you time because the author has done
the tedious work of searching catalogs and indexes to find information on the topic. Many bibliographies also contain 
evaluations of the works that they mention.  

<P>

<DL>

<DT><kbd>ML 156.4.J3 A45 1994</kbd><br>
ed. Wynn, Ron. <strong>All Music Guide to Jazz : the Best CDs, Albums & Tapes</strong>. 1994.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 156.4.P6 T8</kbd><br>
Tudor, Dean. <strong>Black Music</strong>. 1979.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 128.B45 F6 1983</kbd><br>
Floyd, Samuel A. <strong>Black Music in the United States : An Annotated Bibliography of Selected Reference and Research Materials</strong>. 1983.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 128.B45 D44</kbd><br>
De Lerma, Dominique-Rene. <strong>Bibliography of Black Music</strong>. 1981-1984.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 128.J3 M4</kbd><br>
Merriam, Alan P. <strong>A Bibliography of Jazz</strong>. 1954.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 156.4.P6 R88 1989</kbd><br>
Rust, Brian A. L. <strong>The Complete Entertainment Discography, from 1897 to 1942</strong>. 1989.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 156.4.J3 H33 1984</kbd>
Harrison, Max, et. al <strong>The Essential Jazz Records</strong>. 1984.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 128.J3 G7 1991</kbd><br>
Gray, John <strong>Fire Music : a Bibliography of the New Jazz 1959-1990</strong>. 1991.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 128.J3 C4</kbd><br>
Carl Gregor, Duke of Mecklenburg. <strong>International Jazz Bibliography; Jazz Books from 1919 to 1968</strong>. 1969.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 156.4.J3 L67 1992</kbd><br>
Lord, Tom. <strong>The Jazz Discography</strong>. 1992.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 156.4.J3 R9 1978</kbd><br>
Rust, Brian A. L. <strong>Jazz Records, 1897-1942</strong>. 1978.
<DD>*** comments ***

<P>

<DT><kbd>ML 156.4.J3 J47 1980z</kbd><br>
ed. Raben, Erik. <strong>Jazz Records, 1942-80 : a Discography</strong>. [198?].
<DD>*** comments ***

