<CENTER><H1>Sociology and Anthropology 110 - Introduction to Anthropology</H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H4>Winter 1997, Prof. Jerome Levi</H4></center><br>


<H3>Muse - Online Catalog</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="/muse/muse.html">About Muse</A>
<LI><A HREF="telnet://muse.library.carleton.edu">Jump Directly to Muse</A> 
</UL>

<H3>Electronic Indexes and Abstracts</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="/electronic/CD-ROM/CD-ROM.html#am">America:  History & Life</A> (CD-ROM) 
<LI><A HREF="/electronic/online/anl.html">Anthropological Literature</A>
<LI><A HREF="/electronic/CD-ROM/CD-ROM.html#ehraf">Electronic Human Relations Area Files</A> (CD-ROM)
<LI><A HREF="/electronic/CD-ROM/CD-ROM.html#ethnic">Ethnic NewsWatch</A> (CD-ROM)
