<DT><strong>U.S. Government Publications</strong> 3rd Level in <kbd>SI</kbd>
<DD><strong>Smithsonian Institution Publications</strong>.

</DL>

To identify which Latin American-related periodicals are owned by the Gould Library, perform the following steps on
Muse:
<P>
<OL>
<LI><STRONG><KBD>N > NUMBERS</KBD></STRONG>
<LI><STRONG><KBD>C > CALL numbers (Library of Congress)</KBD></STRONG> (use <STRONG><KBD>PER</KBD></STRONG>)
<LI><STRONG><KBD>L > LIMIT this Search</KBD></STRONG>
<LI><STRONG><KBD>S > Words in the SUBJECT</KBD></STRONG>
<LI>(use <STRONG><KBD>latin america*</KBD></STRONG>)
<LI><STRONG><KBD>F > Find items with above limits</KBD></STRONG>
</OL>
