<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Carleton College Library</h3>
<h2 align=center>INTERLIBRARY SERVICES</h2>
<h3>Contact Information</h3>
<p>
InterLibrary Services<br>
Gould Library<br>
Carleton College<br>
1 N College St<br>
Northfield MN 55057-4097<br>
USA<br>
+1-507-646-4257 voice<br>
+1-507-646-4087 FAX<br>
<a href="http://www.library.carleton.edu/ils/">http://www.library.carleton.edu/ils/</a><br>
<br>
OCLC Symbol: <strong>MNN</strong>

<h3>Lending Policies for other libraries</h3>
<ul>
<li>Accept Requests Via: OCLC, FAX, ALA forms
<li>Schedule: n/a (open year-round)
<li>Billing Method: Invoiced with material (no IFM)
<li>Loans:
<ul>
<li>Loan Period: 6 weeks
<li>Renewal Period: No renewals
<li>Charges: $10 per request, but Free to MII, Oberlin Group, US Federal Government libraries
<li>Noncirculating: microforms (exception: MII), reference, periodicals, newspapers, other
</ul>
<li>Copies:
<ul>
<li>Charge for estimates: n/a
<li>Photocopy: Charges same as loans
<li>Microform/Photocopy: Charges same as loans
<li>Microfilm: n/a
<li>Fiche/Fiche: n/a
</ul>
<li>Dissertations: n/a
<li>Theses: n/a
<li>Other:
<ul>
<li>Will lend to USA, Canada, Mexico only
</ul>
</ul>


