<head>
<title>Information Desk</title>
</head>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<center><H1>Information Desk</H1></center>
<p>
Basic information about the library (primarily locational assistance) is
available at the <STRONG>Information Desk</STRONG> located in the library lobby.  Library
para-professional staff and student employees occupy this Information Desk
78 per week when classes are in session.  Telephone inquiries about library
services can be made to the Information Desk number at <STRONG>646-5862</STRONG>.
<P>
During the academic year, the Information Desk is staffed at 
the following times:
<PRE>
<STRONG>
                 Monday-Friday               9 a.m. - 11 p.m.

                 Saturday                    9 a.m. -  5 p.m.

                 Sunday                     10 a.m. - 11 p.m.
</STRONG>
</PRE>
If you have more complex or in-depth 
information needs, the person staffing the Information Desk will refer to the
<A HREF="refdesk.html">Reference Desk</A> to confer with a 
<A HREF="/staff/staffdir.html#ref">professional librarian</A>.
<P>
