<TITLE>Carleton College Reference Question Page</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">

<CENTER><H2>Send a Question to a Librarian</H2></CENTER>

Do you have a question you'd like to have answered by a reference librarian?  Leave 
us your question and we'll do our best to respond to it within 24 hours or less.  Of 
course, you're always welcome to send questions to any member of our 
<A HREF="/staff/staffdir.html#ref">professional staff</A> at any time.
<P>
