<HEAD>
<TITLE>Carleton College Library HTML and Web Site Resource: High Quality HTML Techniques
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<HR SIZE=7>
<CENTER><H1>High Quality HTML Techniques</H1></CENTER>
<HR SIZE=3>
<P>
<A NAME="ho"></A><font size=+2>High Quality HTML Techniques</font> is a quick tour
through a summary of basic Netscape enhancements to HTML.  For more information, see 
Netscape's <A HREF="http://www.netscape.com/assist/net_sites/html_extensions.html">
Extensions to HTML 2.0</A> and <A HREF="http://www.netscape.com/assist/net_sites/html_extensions_3.html">
Extensions to HTML 3.0</A>,
and <A HREF="http://www.netscape.com/assist/net_sites/impact_docs/index.html">High Impact Documents</A> pages.
<P>
<UL>
    <LI>Netscape Specific HTML Enhancements and HTML 3.0
        <UL>
		<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#list">control over "list" elements</A>
		<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#image">image:</A> <UL>
		<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#imalign">alignment</A>
		<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#imsize">sizing</A>
		<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#imborder">borders</A>
		<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#imspace">spacing</A>
		</UL>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#center">centering</A>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#font">fonts</A>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#hr">horizontal rule options</A>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#char">character formats</A>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#foot">footnotes</A>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#sound">sounds</A>
	<LI><A HREF="bnetscape.html#color">colors</A>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#align">alignment</A>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#marq">marquees</A>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#ban">banners</A>
	<LI><A HREF="netscape.html#fig">figures</A>
</UL>
<P>
    <LI>Netscape HTML Enhancements for Graphics
        <UL>
        <LI><A HREF="advancenetscape.html#tables">tables</A>
        <LI><A HREF="advancenetscape.html#back">backgrounds</A>
        <LI><A HREF="advancenetscape.html#fore">foregrounds</A>
        <LI><A HREF="advancenetscape.html#imsize">image size</A>
        <LI><A HREF="advancenetscape.html#flips">low/high resolution flips</A>
        </UL>
<P>
    <LI>Quality HTML Authoring
        <UL>
        <LI><A HREF="quality.html#element">essential elements</A> of a well-designed page
        <LI><A HREF="quality.html#design">design consistency</A>
        <LI><A HREF="quality.html#nav">navigating with buttons/icons/links</A>
        <LI><A HREF="quality.html#type">Web typography</A>
        <LI><A HREF="quality.html#practical">practical considerations</A>
        <LI><A HREF="quality.html#tricks">tricks to control page format</A>
        <LI><A HREF="quality.html#val">markup validation</A>
        </UL>
<P>
    <LI><A HREF="stylish.html">Additional Resources for Creating Stylish HTML Documents</A>

</UL>
<P>
