<CENTER><H1>Creating Your Own Web Site - Outline</H1></CENTER>
<HR size=3>
<P>
<A NAME="ho"></A><font size=+2>Creating Your Own Web Site</font> is a quick tour
through the process of establishing a Web site.
<P>
<UL>
    <LI>Creating Your Own Web Site
        <P>
        <UL>
        <LI>Planning Your Web Site
            <P>
            <UL>
            <LI><A HREF="siteplan.html#purp">Discovering your purpose</A>
            <LI><A HREF="siteplan.html#who">Who needs to be involved? - service providers vs. do-it-yourself</A>
            <LI><A HREF="siteplan.html#onli">How online presence differs from print identity</A>
            <LI><A HREF="siteplan.html#grap">Online graphics considerations</A>
            <LI><A HREF="siteplan.html#plan">Planning site architecture</A>
            <LI><A HREF="siteplan.html#pub">Publicizing your site:  If you build it, will they come?</A>
            </UL>
            <BR>
            <BR>
       <LI>Designing Your Web Site
