<CENTER><H1>Designing Your Web Site</H1></CENTER>

<STRONG>
<OL>
    <LI><A HREF="informed.html">Get Informed:</A></STRONG>
        <P>
        <OL>
         <LI>Figure out <A HREF="informed.html#heck">what the heck the World Wide Web <I>is</I>.</A>
         <LI>Look at how <A HREF="informed.html#other">other organizations</A> are using it.
         <LI>Figure out <A HREF="informed.html#how">how <I>you</I> want to use it.</A>
        </OL> 
    <BR>
    <BR>
    <STRONG><LI><A HREF="learn.html">Learn How to Build Web Pages</A>
    <P>	
    <LI><A HREF="findserver.html">Find a Server and Get Your Pages Published</A>
    <P>
    <LI><A HREF="siteplan.html#pub">Tell the World about Your Home Page</A>
</OL>
