<CENTER><H1>Web Building Resources</H1></CENTER>
<STRONG>
<A HREF="#browsers">Browsers</A><BR>
<A HREF="#HTMLtools">HTML Tools</A><BR>
<A HREF="#graphics">Learning about Graphics</A><BR>
<A HREF="#servers">Servers</A><BR>
<A HREF="#publicize">Publicizing Your Page</A><BR>
<A HREF="#lists">Great Resource Lists</A><BR>

</STRONG>
<P>
<FONT SIZE="-1">Note that some of these resources automatically download the program.  If you you haven't 
ever downloaded files from the Net, use this link to get <A HREF="ftp.html"><STRONG>help</STRONG></A>.<p>
If you notice that any of the links to resources listed here no longer work, or hear about a great update or
resource that should be listed here, please send me mail at <A HREF="mailto:temetz@carleton.edu">
temetz@carleton.edu</A>.</FONT>
<P>
<HR>
<P>
<A NAME="browsers"></A><H3>Browsers</H3>
<UL>
<DL>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.browserwatch.iworld.com/">BrowserWatch</A>
<DD>A leading site for information about Web browsers and plug-ins.
</DL>
</UL>
<p>
<p><em><A HREF="#contents">Return to Contents</A></em>
<HR>
<A NAME="HTMLtools"></A><H3>HTML Tools</H3>
<UL>
<DL>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.awa.com/nct/software/webtools.html">HTML Developers' Tools Library</A>
<DD>Compiled by the editors of the <A HREF="http://www.awa.com/nct/software/aboutweb.html">Web Developer's Journal</A>. 
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.best.com/~wooldri/tools/tools.html">HTML Tools List</A>
<DD>Compiled by the <A HREF="http://www.hwg.org/">HTML Writers Guild</A>.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.comvista.com/net/www/WWWDirectory.html">Macintosh WWW Development Resources</A>
<DD>A rich resource for Macintosh enthusiasts from Com Vista.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.nas.nasa.gov/NAS/WebWeavers/index.html">Tools for Aspiring Web Weavers</A>
<DD>Brought to you by a Webmaster at NASA.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.kosone.com/people/nelson/nl.htm">The Web Designer</A>
<DD>HTML and Web design resource site from Nelson Laviolette, including a lengthy list of HTML tools.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www59.metronet.com/dev/">Web Engineer's Toolbox</A>
<DD>
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.utoronto.ca/webdocs/HTMLdocs/">Web Software Tools List</A>
<DD>by <A HREF="http://www.utoronto.ca/ian/ian-home.html">Ian Graham</A> 
				(University of Toronto) 
</DL>
</UL>
<p><em><A HREF="#contents">Return to Contents</A></em>	
