		    <LI><A HREF="http://www.cowan.edu.au/ecuwis/docs/ecudocs/images.html">The Creative Internet: 
				Transparent Image Info</A>
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.execpc.com/inp/imaging.html">Imaging from InterNetworking Publishing</A>
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.algonet.se/~dip/minimal1.htm">Digital Picture Guide (from Sweden)</A>
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.public.iastate.edu/~stark/gutil_sv.html">The Graphic Utilities' Site & Version FAQ</A>
			<LI><A HREF=" http://vancouver-webpages.com/image-tips/image-test.html">Inline Image Capability Test</A>
		</UL>
		<P>
		<LI>Tutorials
