                        <LI><a href="http://www.yahoo.com/Computers/World_Wide_Web/Programming/Icons">Yahoo Server: Icons</a>
                        <LI><a href="http://www-ns.rutgers.edu/doc-images/">Network Services WWW Icons and Logos</a>
