                        <LI><a href="http://www.cs.indiana.edu/elisp/w3/icons.html">List of Standard Icons and Symbols</a>
                        <LI><a href="http://www.nosc.mil/planet_earth/images.html">Planet Earth Images and Icons</a>
                        <LI><a href="http://ivory.nosc.mil/html/trancv/html/icons-hcc.html">Icon Archive - Trancv 1</a>  
                        <LI><a href="http://ivory.nosc.mil/html/trancv/html/icons-bsdi.html">Icon Archive - Trancv 2</a>
