				     <LI>Flag Archives
			         <UL>
                        <LI><a href="http://www.yahoo.com/Reference/Flags/">Yahoo Server: Flags</a>
                        <LI>Two (probably incomplete) collections of world flags, an <a href="http://www.adfa.oz.au/CS/flg/old.html">old collection</a>, and a <a href="http://www.adfa.oz.au/CS/flags/">newer collection</a>, both by Christopher J.S. Vance.
                        <LI><a href="http://155.187.10.12/images/flags/">Index of Flags</a>
                        <LI><a href="http://155.187.10.12/flags/flags.html">Flags</a></dl><p>
                     </UL>
                </UL>
          </UL>
