<DD>Links to information about various types of Web servers.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://scholar2.lib.vt.edu/handbook/handbook.html">Managing a WWW Service</A>
<DD>The University of Vermont offers some points to consider about running your own Web server.
</DL>
</UL>
