<P>
<A NAME="lists"></A><H3>Great Resource Lists</H3>
<UL>
<DL>

<DT><A HREF="http://ecco.bsee.swin.edu.au/text/masters/masters.html">Bob Allison's Web Masters' Page</A>
<DD>A comprehensive resource to Web authoring which is an expanded version of his
    Tips for Web Spinners resource.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://ncdesign.kyushu-id.ac.jp/">HTML Design Guide</A>
<DD> From C&P Network Communication Design in Japan.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://members.aol.com/htmlguru/index.html">The HTML Guru!</A>
<DD>Resources for webmasters, HTML authors, server administrators, and anyone involved in Web
    site creation and management.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.hwg.org/">HTML Writers Guild</A>
<DD>One of the world's leading organizations serving the informational, educational, 
    and support needs of HTML designers.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.itcs.com/topten/devres.html">ITCS WWW Development Resources</A>
<DD>Compiled by a commerical Internet consulting service.
<P> 
<DT><A HREF="stylish.html">Resources for Creating Stylish HTML Documents</A>
<DD>From Section III of this Tutorial.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.awa.com/nct/software/eleclea.html">Web Developer's Journal</A>
<DD>News and reviews of the latest hypertext authoring tools, browsers, etc.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://WWW.Stars.com/">The Web Developer's Virtual Library</A>
<DD>Thousands (literally) of links to Web developer resources, as well as articles, demos, graphics. 
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www59.metronet.com/dev/">The Web Engineer's Toolbox</A>
<DD>This site contains useful tools for anyone involved in Web Development.
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://union.ncsa.uiuc.edu:80/HyperNews/get/www/html/guides.html">Web Mastery Forums and Resource Lists</A>
<DD>Created by Daniel LaLiberte.

<DT><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Computers_and_Internet/Internet/World_Wide_Web/Authoring/">
     Yahoo Index: World Wide Web Authoring</A>
<DD>A lifetime's amount of information...
<P>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.boutell.com/faq/">World Wide Web FAQ</A>
<DD>Maintained by Boutell.Com, Inc.
</DL>
</UL>
