<CENTER><H1>Books About HTML and Web Site Development</H1></CENTER>
<HR SIZE=3>
<P>

<DL>
    <DD>All-in-one Web surfing & publishing kit Windows/CD-ROM ed. Scottsdale, AZ : Coriolis Group, 1995.
<P>

    <DT>Angell, David and Brent Heslop.
    <DD><A href="http://www.northcoast.com/savetz/booklist/business_marketing/angell_internet_business_companion_the.html">The Internet Business Companion: Growing Your Business in the Electronic Age.</a>  (Reading, MA :  Addison-Wesley, c1995).
<P>
    <DT>Aronson, Larry.
    <DD><A HREF="http://www.users.interport.net/~laronson/HTML_TOC.html">HTML Manual of Style</A> / (Emeryville, CA :  Ziff-Davis Press, c1994).
<P>
    <DT>Aronson, Larry.
    <DD><A HREF="http://www.users.interport.net/~laronson/html3mos.html">HTML 3 Manual of Style</A> / (Emeryville, CA :  Ziff-Davis Press, c1995).
<P>
    <DT>Ause, Wayne.
    <DD><A HREF="http://www.mcp.com/209173161858510/cgi-bin/bag?isbn=1-56276-363-6&last=/bookstore">Instant HTML Web pages</A> / Emeryville, Calif. : Ziff-Davis Press, 1995.
<P>
