    <DT>Flynn, Peter.
    <DD><A HREF="http://www.ucc.ie/~pflynn/books/wwwbook.html">The World Wide Web handbook : a guide for users, authors, and publishers</A> / London ; Boston : International Thomson Computer Press, 1995.
