<P>
    <DT>Franks, Mike.
    <DD><A HREF="http://www.sscnet.ucla.edu:80/ssc/franks/book/">Internet publishing handbook</A> / Reading, Mass. : Addison-Wesley, 1995.
<P>
    <DT>Fry, Andrew.
    <DD><a href="http://www.socialstudies.com/zenger/13/WAR147.html">How to publish on the Internet : a comprehensive step-by-step guide to creative expression on the  World Wide Web </a>/ New York : Warner Books, 1995.
