<DOCHDR>
http://www.library.carleton.edu:80/electronic/cd-rom/cd-rom.html 137.22.11.46 19970217121024 text/html 13230
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.3.2 ID/3754
