<p><hr><p>
<center><b>Welcome to my very own home page!</b><p><p></center>
My name is Josh Mitchell, and I'm a senior at <a href="http://www.carleton.edu/">Carleton College</a> in Northfield, MN.  I work in the <a href="http://www.library.carleton.edu">Laurence McKinley Gould Library</a>, better known as the Libe.  If you'd like to get in touch with me in the real world, you can write to me at:<p>
<p>
Josh Mitchell <br>
300 N. College St. <br>
Northfield, MN 55057 <p>
or call me at 507-645-1393.<p>
Conversely, you could send me email at <a href="mailto:mitchelj@carleton.edu">mitchelj@carleton.edu.</a>

