<h2>Celena Peet</h2>
<hr size=3>
Celena is a Medieval history major from Hubbard, Iowa. She actually works for
Carolyn Sanford as special projects manager. There isn't a picture of her, or anything
else interesting for that matter, because she
is too busy dealing with the Laurence McKinley Gould Exhibit:
<p>
<br clear=all>
<center><a href="/Gould/index.html"><img src="gouldplans.gif"></a></center>
<br clear=all>
<p>
<center>Maybe you should go there instead. She thinks it's cool.</center>

