<H1>ED ZAMORA'S HOMEPAGE</H1>

<IMG SRC=rsat_work.GIF ALT="[IMAGE: at work icon]">
This page is currently under construction.
<hr noshade>
<p>	
Basically, I'm still learning how to write a web page in the first place, so
any psycho bored enought to look here should chill...

Let's see, what is interesting about me... actually, not much, but here it goes:
<p>
I am currently a Junior biology major attending Carleton College, MN.  I am also working on getting my butt to Med school.  Like most college bound students, I spent my 1st year figuring out what I wanted and the rest of my time partying: (place pic here) Currently I am working on figuring out how I ended up in state where there are only two seasons--the freezing blight called winter and the humid mosquito breeding seasons.
<p>
For fun I have numerous little diversions including:

<h2>HOCKEY!</h2><ul>
<li><A href="http://www.yahoo.com/Recreation/Sports/Hockey/NHL___National_Hockey
_League/">Yahoo:NHL</a><br>
<li>The Official <a href="http://www.nhl.com/">NHL Home Page</a><br>
</ul>
