<BODY>
<H1><CENTER>CD ROMS from the U.S. Government </CENTER>
</H1>
<P><CENTER>Carleton College Electronic Media Bibliography </CENTER>
<P><HR><HR><STRONG>Please note that this list is a work in progress. <A HREF="suggest.html">Comments
</A>are welcomed.</STRONG>. <BR>
<BR>
We are also interested in recieving information about <A HREF="error.html">errors
or additions</A>. <HR>
<H2>Introduction</H2>
This document is an annotated list of all of the CD-ROM products received
by the Government Documents Department of Carleton College Library. The
Table of Contents below provides titles and SuDoc numbers. Clicking on the
title will lead you to the annotation. Annotations include a description
of the contents, file format, machine requirments, the availability of software
and documentation. In addition some items contain links to the abstracts
or other documentation. <HR>See <A HREF="whatsnew.html">what's new</A> from
GPO<BR>
Also see a list of <A HREF="microdata.html">Microdata</A> files and <A HREF="enviroment.html">enviromental</A>
files. <HR><!--Do add line breaks to the below-->
