<HTML>
<HEAD>
   <TITLE>Current Contents</TITLE>
   <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Mozilla/3.0Gold (Win95; I) [Netscape]">
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Current Contents</H1>

<P><B>Current Contents</B> reprints tables of contents from over 6,600
journals in all disciplines. It contains content data (article title, authors,
journal name, etc) and abstracts from articles in over 6,600 different
journals. The database is updated weekly; thus the information is in the
database at about the same time the publication reaches the readers. Coverage
includes the most recent 52 weeks. </P>

<P>There is a very broad range of journal coverage, including: agriculture,
biology and environmental sciences; social and behavioral sciences; clinical
medicine; engineering, technology and applied sciences; life sciences;
and arts and humanities. </P>

<P>You must have a <A HREF="http://www.library.carleton.edu:8001/currentpswd.html">username
and password</A> to access Current Contents.</P>

<P>Two other online database available from the Carleton Library, <A HREF="http://www.library.carleton.edu/electronic/online/uncover.html">UnCover</A>
and the <A HREF="http://www.oclc.org/oclc/man/6928fsdb/general/general1.htm#contents1st">Contents1st</A>
database in <A HREF="http://www.library.carleton.edu/electronic/online/firstsearch.html">FirstSearch</A>,
also allow you to browse the tables of contents of thousands of journals.
</P>

<P><A HREF="http://cutter.lib.umn.edu:80/~minitex/">MINITEX</A> is making
Current Contents available via the World Wide Web on a free <B>trial</B>
basis for MINITEX participants through June 1996. Current Contents gopher
access ceased on June 4. </P>

<CENTER><P>For more information about Current Contents, ask a Librarian,
or connect to Current Contents on the Web, select one of the Current Contents
databases, and click on the <B>Help on Searching</B> button. <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="http://othello.lib.umn.edu/cgi-bin/webspirs.sh?sp.nextform=top.htm">Jump
Directly to Current Contents Web Access Now</A></B> </P></CENTER>

<P>
<HR></P>

<CENTER><P><A HREF="http://www.library.carleton.edu/electronic/online/index.html">Return
to the Online Databases Page</A> <BR>
<BR>
<I>Maintained by Scott Salzman, <A HREF="mailto:ssalzman@carleton.edu">ssalzman@carleton.edu<BR>
</A>Last updated: September 18, 1996 </I></P></CENTER>

</BODY>
</HTML>

