</DOCHDR>
<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Carleton College LiBRary HTML and Web Site Resource: Making a Simple Netscape Table
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY  BGCOLOR=#FFFFF>
<HR SIZE=7>
<CENTER><H1>Making A Simple Netscape Table</H1></CENTER>
<HR size=3>
There are an almost bewildering array of tags available to create a table 
which can be read by Netscape's Browser.  Most of the tags serve to make minute
adjustments in table appearance.  Tables can be this simple:<P><OL>
<LI>Use the <TT>&lt;TABLE BORDER&gt;</TT> tag.
<LI>Use <TT>&lt;CAPTION&gt;</TT> and <TT>&lt;/CAPTION&gt;</TT> to title the table. (optional)
<LI>Use <TT>&lt;TH&gt;</TT> and <TT>&lt;/TH&gt;</TT> to create column headings
<LI>Work across in rows:<UL>
	<LI>Each row begins with <TT>&lt;TR&gt;</TT>
	<LI>Each item in the row is framed with <TT>&lt;TD&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;</TT>
	<LI>To create row headings, frame the text with <TT>&lt;TD&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;</TT>
	<LI>The row ends with <TT>&lt;/TR&gt;</TT></UL>
<LI>End the list with <TT>&lt;/TABLE&gt;</TT>
</OL>

<HR>
<P>
<STRONG>Example:</STRONG>
<CENTER>
<P>
<TABLE BORDER>
<CAPTION><STRONG>Vegetable Comparison</STRONG></CAPTION>
<TH></TH>
<TH>Peas</TH>
<TH>Carrots</TH>
<TH>Onions</TH>
<TR>
<TD><STRONG>Color</STRONG></TD>
<TD>Green</TD>
<TD>Orange</TD>
<TD>White or yellow</TD>
</TR>
<TR>
<TD><STRONG>Shape</STRONG></TD>
<TD>round</TD>
<TD>cone</TD>
<TD>round</TD>
</TR>
<TR>
<TD><STRONG>Location</STRONG></TD>
<TD>above ground</TD>
<TD>below ground</TD>
<TD>below ground</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE></P><P>
</CENTER> 
<P><BR><BR>
<STRONG>Came from this HTML:</STRONG><P><TT>
&lt;TABLE BORDER&gt;<BR>
&lt;CAPTION&gt;&lt;B&gt;Vegetable Comparison&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/CAPTION&gt;<BR>
&lt;TH&gt;&lt;/TH&gt;<BR>
&lt;TH&gt;Peas&lt;/TH&gt;<BR>
&lt;TH&gt;Carrots&lt;/TH&gt;<BR>
&lt;TH&gt;Onions&lt;/TH&gt;<BR>
&lt;TR&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;&lt;B&gt;Color&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;Green&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;Orange&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;White or yellow&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;/TR&gt;<BR>
&lt;TR&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;&lt;B&gt;Shape&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;round&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;cone&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;round&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;/TR&gt;<BR>
&lt;TR&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;&lt;B&gt;Location&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;above ground&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;Below ground&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;TD&gt;Below ground&lt;/TD&gt;<BR>
&lt;/TR&gt;<BR>
&lt;/TABLE&gt;<BR></TT>

<P>
<HR SIZE=7>
