<TITLE>Carleton College Library HTML and Web Site Resource: Learn How to Build Web Pages
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<hr size=7>
<CENTER><H1>Learn How to Build Web Pages</H1></CENTER>
Nearly everything you need to know about building Web pages can be learned from resources <EM>already available on the Web itself!</EM>
<HR>
<UL>
		<LI>Specifications
		<UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.w3.org/pub/WWW/MarkUp/html-spec/">HTML 2.0 Specification</A>
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.hp.co.uk/people/dsr/html3/Contents.html">HTML 3.0 Specification Draft</A>
      <LI><A HREF= "http://www.w3.org/pub/WWW/MarkUp/Wilbur/">Proposed HTML 3.2 Specification</A>
		</UL>
		<P>
		<LI>Online Documentation
		<UL><LI><A HREF="http://www.ncsa.uiuc.edu/General/Internet/WWW/HTMLPrimer.html">NCSA Beginners Guide </a> 
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.cosy.sbg.ac.at/www-doku/html/index.html">Writing html</A> By Brigitte Jellinek, 
				Salzburg Univ
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.ncsa.uiuc.edu/demoweb/url-primer.html">A Beginner's Guide to URLs</A>
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.utoronto.ca/webdocs/HTMLdocs/NewHTML/intro.html">HTML Documentation</A> 
			by <A HREF="http://www.utoronto.ca/ian/ian-home.html">Ian Graham</A> 
				(U of Toronto).
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.ncsa.uiuc.edu:80/SDG/Software/Mosaic/Docs/fill-out-forms/overview.html">HTML Forms Documentation and Tutorial</A>
		    <LI><A HREF="http://members.aol.com/htmlguru/transparent_images.html"> Transparent Image Info from the HTML Guru</A>
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.best.com/~adamb/GIFpage.html">Transparent/Interlaced GIF Resource</A>
			<LI><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Computers_and_Internet/Internet/World_Wide_Web/Imagemaps/">Yahoo's imagemap Resource</A> 
		</UL>
		<P>
		<LI>Online Tutorials 
		<UL><li><A HREF="http://ecco.bsee.swin.edu.au/text/html-tut/intro.html">HTML Tutorial</A> -- learning the basics.
		<LI><A HREF="http://www.ncsa.uiuc.edu:80/SDG/Software/Mosaic/Docs/fill-out-forms/overview.html">HTML Forms Documentation and Tutorial</A>
		<LI><A HREF="http://www59.metronet.com/dev/ismaps/">Graphical imagemap Tutorial</A>	
	    <LI>Larger list of <A HREF="resources.html">Web Building Resources</A>
		<P>
		</UL>
		<LI>Books
		<UL>
		<LI><A HREF="bib.html">A Bibliography of HTML and Web Site Books</A>
	</UL>
</UL>
