<TITLE>CD-ROMS from the Bureau of Economic Analysis</TITLE>

</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H2>
CD-ROMS from the Bureau of Economic Analysis
</H2>
<HR SIZE="6">
<HR>

 <H3>
<A NAME="RTFToC83">REGIONAL
ECONOMIC INFORMATION SYSTEM.
</A></H3>
<H4>
<A NAME="RTFToC84">
C 59.24:991; 992; 993/update
</A></H4>
<P>
Bureau of Economic Analysis, 1991- .
<P>
Data from 3,107 counties and 337 metropolitan areas for 1969-89. Includes
personal and per capita income, regional economic profiles, farm income and
expenses, full and part-time employment and earnings by SIC industry, etc. Also
included: BEARFACTS, which are one page descriptions of economic developments
in an area, and journey-to-work data.
<UL>
<LI>File format: ISO 9660.
<LI>Compatible: PC.
<LI>Paper Copy: State-level data published in C 59.2:IN4/989. State Personal
Income: 1929-87.
<LI>Documentation: On Disc 

</UL><P>
