<H3><A NAME="RTFToC120"></A>NHIS, the NATIONAL HEALTH INTERVIEW SURVEY.
</H3>
<H4><A NAME="RTFToC121"></A>HE 20.6209/4-3:10/1-6. </H4>
Health and Human Services Department, National Center for Health Statistics,
1990- . <BR>
<BR>
This statistical file contains interview results from a nationally representative
sample of 125,000 persons in each sample year, beginning in 1987. The discs
cover health topics from the NHIS Basic Questionnaire, including acute and
chronic conditions, injuries, hospital stays, etc. These CDs also includes
the 1987 NHIS Special Health Topics, such as cancer risk factors and cancer
epidemiology, polio, and adoption. 
<UL>
  <LI>File format: SETS 
  <LI>Compatible: PC. 
  <LI>Documentation: Complete on line Documentation 
  <UL>
    <LI>SETS USER REFERENCE MANUAL printed from disc 
  </UL>
</UL>
