Optional format.  The Lambert Azimuthal Equal Area projection was chosen for
the data on this disc and the Advanced Very High Resolution Radiometer (AVHRR)
biweekly composites CD-ROM's.

<P>
If you are interested in obtaining more information on the availability of data, 
then call 1-800-usamaps.  If you have access to a network system, then you can
check out the USGS Federal Geographic Data Committee (FGDC) Geospatial Data 
Clearinghouse server node at the url "http://nsdi.usgs.gov/nsdi/index.html".
