the data.  The seismic database may be searched by shot point location, velocity data index, 
time/velocity/depth, line intersections, line length, number of data records, field recording 
parameters, and trace number to CDP to shot point conversion tables. The well database may be 
searched by well location, well drilling histories (when started and when completed), total depth, 
and depths to 16 selected rock units.
