<A NAME="waterfowl">
WATERFOWL MANAGEMENT HANDBOOK</A>
</H3>
<H4>
I 49.108:W29/CD
</H4>
<P>
National Biological Service
<P>
This CD contains all of the waterfowl maganagemnt lhandbook leaflets though April 1995<UL>
<LI>
The disc does not come with the software necessary to access the data.
