<TITLE>US Department of Justice CD ROM Index</TITLE>

</HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER><H2>
CD ROMS from the US Department of Justice
</H2>
Carleton College Government Documents Electronic Media List</CENTER>
<HR SIZE="6">

<HR><H3>
<A NAME="RTFToC184">
NATIONAL CRIMINAL JUSTICE REFERENCE SERVICE DOCUMENT DATA BASE
</A>
</H3>
<H4>
<A NAME="RTFToC185">
J 28.31/2:994;994-2;995
</A>
</H4>
<P>
U.S. Department of Justice
<P>
718-D-1 94-042-E
<P>
This CD is a bibliographic cititation database with abstacts for documents related to the justice system. It 
contains bibliographic information on over 125,000 items for the period 1972-1995. About 6,000 new items are 
added to the data base each year. This CD is to be updated every six months.
<P>
All documents are available through interlibrary loan for domestic U.S. users and foreign International Document 
Exchange (IDE) users. The cost of interlibrary loan is $4.50. Deposit accounts can be established to pay for 
these services. Additional information can be found by calling 1-800-851-3420 or writing to NCJRS, Box 6000, 
Rockville, MD 20849.
<UL>
<LI>File format: dBase?(Exportable in dBase, Lotus 1-2-3 and several ASCII formats)
<LI>Compatible: DOS, Windows
<LI>Documentation: On Line Help for software.
</UL>
