<A NAME="RTFToC192">
1994 IRS FEDERAL TAX FORMS
</A>
</H3>
<H4>
<A NAME="RTFToC193">
T 22.51/4:994/REL.1;Rel 2;Rel 3;   -995/REL.95-2
</A>
</H4>
<P>
IRS 1994
<P>
Electronic copies of most of the IRS tax forms for the 1994 tax year. With the reader supplied most of the forms 
can be printed, but several(including the 1040 EZ) are supplied in a multi layer format. This means that the gray 
boxes and background found on the forms is supplied separately, and unfortunately in a deep black color, making them 
impossible to print out completely. This is a three CD series, with each disc presumably containing more forms than 
the last.
<UL>
<LI>File format:Adobe Portable Document Format(PDF).
<LI>Compatible: PC or Machintosh.
<LI>Paper copy:
<LI>Access by: Adobe's reader is supplied for each platform
<LI>Documentation: Documenation on disc
<LI>Disc(s):
</UL>

